    <section name="Document type">
      <span class="shortdesc">What is a document type</span>

    <p>A document type is a defintion of the structure of similar documents.
       The documents are similar because they all have the structure defined in 
       the document type. These documents together are the class of documents 
       that have the structure defined in the document type.
   </p>
